reviews.text:
Fantastic mutton soup, ordered the $8 mutton rib soup! The queue is quite long, wait was around 20min-ish, BUT ITS WORTH THE WAIT

The meat is fall-apart tender, with a very pleasant mutton flavour (not too stinky), and the store is quite generous with the amount of meat;

The soup is slightly herbal, very hearty and would go really well on a cold rainy day 🤤
